m\nensemble at a desired temperature. In order to ensure equilibrium sampling, we\ndevelop a hybrid Monte Carlo algorithm that employs cyclic shear as a trial\ngeneration step, and has acceptance probabilities that depend not only on the\nchange in internal energy but also on heat dissipated (equivalently, work\ndone). We show that such an algorithm indeed generates an equilibrium ensemble.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 May 2018 13:57:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Jun 2020 08:37:30 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 25 May 2022 07:35:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-05-26"}
