ronment\nwithout requiring forecasting. The actual effectiveness of the proposed SCBM is\nsupported by extensive energy-vs.-delay performance comparisons, that cover:\n(i) a number of heterogeneous 3G/4G/WiFi FOGRAN scenarios; (ii) synthetic and\nreal-world workloads; and, (iii) MPTCP and SinglePathTCP (SPTCP) wireless\nconnections.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 31 May 2018 15:11:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-01"}
